text: Stefano Patuanelli (born 8 June 1974) is an Italian politician, member of the Five Star Movement. On 5 September 2019 he was appointed Minister of Economic Development in the Conte II Cabinet. == References == Category:Living people Category:1974 births Category:Five Star Movement politicians Category:People from Trieste Category:Conte II Cabinet Category:University of Trieste alumni Category:Government ministers of Italy Category:Senators of Legislature XVIII of Italy Category:Politicians of Friuli-Venezia Giulia
